{"tid":1937274,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"反對根正苗黃論","createTime":"2020-03-21T19:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T21:26:15.000Z","uid":80567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6dd526dc2488ccee534e340ccc2cb09c3569e7","tid":1937274,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T19:38:45.000Z","msg":"無聊起下藍絲底<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1937131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1937131</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家嗰條粉皮May Chan係咪警甴先<br />\n嗱黑警就死全家嘅<br />\n但老豆老母on9愛國藍絲<br />\n就唔代表仔女唔可以係手足、港獨？<br />\n幾多人因為場運動同啲藍絲屋企人反面？<br />\n大把人屋企藍啦<br />\n畀嗰幾件連登仔喺度一碌鳩打沉一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真個May Chan見到你起佢個仔<br />\n萬一個仔係手足<br />\n佢個臭閪只會更興奮，挪喻佢個仔乜剩<br />\n如果樓豬係醒少少就唔好俾attention<br />\n你鍾意起人老母咪起飽佢<br />\n搞個<span style=\"color: red;\">未肯定</span>關事嘅做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n咁樣推根正苗黃法<br />\n遲早釀成更多on9仔捉錯手足<br />\n然後又唔係整痛到藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一打唔使找<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嗱，除非個兒子蔡承東都係藍絲<br />\n咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n有冇DB仔現身說法"},{"pid":"a14cc38c0dd786f77a09c6d9b2ecb9997f79c449","tid":1937274,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T19:49:12.000Z","msg":"似借刀 ...."},{"pid":"c9605a042d081bb59ba046da9f2d08d62487cabf","tid":1937274,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed674f0aa00bc56c44b5f863b5da5aa72306647","tid":1937274,"uid":103243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T21:24:23.000Z","msg":"佢哋要將黃嘅standard推高嘛<br />\n<br />\n依家就要求父母親戚黃<br />\n遲啲連鄰居藍都照批鬥㗎啦"},{"pid":"8d864640820af94957ae7cd2152e25d8ccf8cbb7","tid":1937274,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed674f0aa00bc56c44b5f863b5da5aa72306647","tid":1937274,"uid":103243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T21:24:23.000Z","msg":"佢哋要將黃嘅standard推高嘛<br />\n<br />\n依家就要求父母親戚黃<br />\n遲啲連鄰居藍都照批鬥㗎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T21:26:15.000Z","msg":"個po似私怨 借刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}